<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Sanitation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The quality of the water used in the production of beverage shall meet the requirement of the Quality Standard of Drinking Water.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The caffeine contents of packed beverages shall meet the following requirements:
1.Coffee: Those products labeled as "low caffeine" shall not have more than 2 mg/100mL (20 ppm) caffeine.
2.Tea and cocoa: The caffeine contents shall not exceed 50mg/100mL (500 ppm).Those products labeled as "low caffeine" shall not have more than 2 mg/100mL (20 ppm) caffeine.
3.If beverages, other than tea, coffee and cocoa, contain caffeine, the caffeine contents shall not exceed 32 mg/100mL(320 ppm).]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
